    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. The engine and transmission are fully functional and have been regularly serviced, though the car shows clear signs of age. You can expect some cosmetic wear on the exterior, including minor paint fading and a few small dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and plastic trim. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that runs well and is ready for the road.",
      "price": 19500.0,
